 common/tegra194-camera-d4xx.dtsi   | 447 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 tegra194-p2888-0001-p2822-0000.dts |   5 +-
 2 files changed, 450 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)
